- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with the decidability of model-checking logics of time, knowledge, and probability.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper deals with epistemic semantics, which is a common topic in AI.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possibility as the paper deals with probability and Markov chains, which are commonly used in machine learning.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility as the paper deals with decidability results and mathematical problems.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possibility as the paper deals with model checking, which is a common technique in programming language verification.
